Ayurveda, the ancient science of healing, focuses on balancing the three doshas (Vata, Pitta, and Kapha) to maintain healthy skin. Kerala Ayurveda emphasizes herbal remedies, oils, and natural treatments to nourish and rejuvenate the skin.

"Healthy skin reflects inner wellness. Ayurveda focuses on detoxifying and healing from within."
